title: Episode #39 - Mick Foley & ME w/ special guest Sam "Primetime" Roberts
description: Professional Wrestler, Author, Actor, & Comedian Mick Foley, ME, & special guest Sam "Primetime" Roberts (from the Opie and Anthony Show) hang in the Mancave and talk about Stand-up comedy, Wrestling, and the adult film star Siri.
